NAME: USS Enterprise
DESCRIPTION: The flagship of Starfleet across several generations, known for its exploration and defense missions.

NAME: USS Voyager
DESCRIPTION: A ship lost in the Delta Quadrant attempting to return to Earth, commanded by Captain Janeway.

NAME: USS Defiant
DESCRIPTION: A small but powerful warship specifically designed to combat Dominion threats.

NAME: USS Excelsior
DESCRIPTION: One of the first ships with a transwarp drive, known for its robustness and extended service.

NAME: USS Discovery
DESCRIPTION: A ship equipped with a spore drive capable of instantaneous travel anywhere in the universe.

NAME: USS Reliant
DESCRIPTION: A Miranda-class ship that played a significant role in "Star Trek II: The Wrath of Khan."

NAME: USS Prometheus
DESCRIPTION: An experimental ship capable of splitting into three autonomous sections for combat efficiency.

NAME: USS Equinox
DESCRIPTION: A Nova-class ship that was also dragged into the Delta Quadrant like Voyager.

NAME: USS Grissom
DESCRIPTION: An Oberth-class ship primarily used for scientific and exploration missions.

NAME: USS Shenzhou
DESCRIPTION: A Starfleet ship commanded by Captain Philippa Georgiou in "Star Trek: Discovery."

NAME: USS Saratoga
DESCRIPTION: Several ships have borne this name, known for their support and exploration missions.

NAME: USS Titan
DESCRIPTION: Commanded by Captain William Riker after the events of "Star Trek: Nemesis."

NAME: USS Stargazer
DESCRIPTION: The first ship commanded by Jean-Luc Picard, famous for the "Picard Maneuver."

NAME: USS Yamato
DESCRIPTION: A sister ship to the Enterprise-D, destroyed by an Iconian probe.

NAME: USS Hood
DESCRIPTION: An Excelsior-class ship that appeared frequently in "Star Trek: The Next Generation."

NAME: USS Constellation
DESCRIPTION: A Constellation-class ship commanded by Commodore Matt Decker.

NAME: USS Columbia
DESCRIPTION: One of the early NX-class ships, sister ship to the Enterprise NX-01.

NAME: USS Intrepid
DESCRIPTION: Several ships have borne this name, known for their exploration missions.

NAME: USS Bellerophon
DESCRIPTION: An Intrepid-class ship similar to Voyager, appearing in "Star Trek: Deep Space Nine."

NAME: USS Cairo
DESCRIPTION: A Starfleet ship mentioned in various episodes of "Star Trek: The Next Generation."

NAME: Millennium Falcon
DESCRIPTION: A YT-1300 light freighter piloted by Han Solo and Chewbacca, known for its speed and unique modifications.

NAME: Star Destroyer
DESCRIPTION: A powerful capital ship used by the Galactic Empire, known for its triangular shape and heavy armament.

NAME: X-Wing
DESCRIPTION: A versatile starfighter used by the Rebel Alliance, known for its X-shaped wings and agility in combat.

NAME: TIE Fighter
DESCRIPTION: The standard starfighter of the Galactic Empire, known for its distinctive twin ion engines and hexagonal wings.

NAME: Death Star
DESCRIPTION: A massive space station and superweapon capable of destroying entire planets, used by the Galactic Empire.

NAME: Slave I
DESCRIPTION: A Firespray-31-class patrol and attack craft piloted by the bounty hunter Boba Fett.

NAME: Nebulon-B Frigate
DESCRIPTION: A versatile medical and escort frigate used by the Rebel Alliance.

NAME: Mon Calamari Cruiser
DESCRIPTION: A large capital ship used by the Rebel Alliance, known for its distinctive organic design.

NAME: A-Wing
DESCRIPTION: A high-speed starfighter used by the Rebel Alliance, known for its speed and agility.

NAME: B-Wing
DESCRIPTION: A heavy assault starfighter used by the Rebel Alliance, known for its unique gyroscopic cockpit and heavy weaponry.

NAME: Imperial Shuttle
DESCRIPTION: A transport shuttle used by the Galactic Empire, often for transporting high-ranking officials.

NAME: Executor
DESCRIPTION: The Super Star Destroyer flagship of Darth Vader, known for its massive size and firepower.

NAME: Y-Wing
DESCRIPTION: A durable starfighter-bomber used by the Rebel Alliance, known for its versatility in combat.

NAME: Ebon Hawk
DESCRIPTION: A Dynamic-class freighter used by Revan in the "Knights of the Old Republic" series.

NAME: Arc-170
DESCRIPTION: A heavy starfighter used by the Galactic Republic during the Clone Wars, known for its firepower and durability.

NAME: Venator-class Star Destroyer
DESCRIPTION: A versatile capital ship used by the Galactic Republic during the Clone Wars.

NAME: Ghost
DESCRIPTION: A modified VCX-100 light freighter used by the crew of the Ghost in the "Star Wars Rebels" series.

NAME: Razor Crest
DESCRIPTION: A gunship used by the Mandalorian bounty hunter Din Djarin in "The Mandalorian" series.

NAME: Droid Control Ship
DESCRIPTION: A Lucrehulk-class battleship used by the Trade Federation to control droid armies during the Clone Wars.

NAME: Outrider
DESCRIPTION: A modified YT-2400 light freighter piloted by Dash Rendar in the "Shadows of the Empire" multimedia project.
